      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "If the Northern Pacific Railway\ncompany doesn't stop driving piles\nacross Madelia street. the city Of\nfcials declare they will take steps to\nenjoin the company from proceeding\nin the work now going on where that\nthoroughfare crosses the tracks.\n\n\nFor some time past the company\nhas been preparing to widen its\ntracks in the east end of town, and\nin doing so have driven the pilngs\nsquarely across Madelia street.\n\n\nA meeting between the city Of\nficials, consisting OF Mayor Daggett,\nCommissioner Handley. City Engineer"
